Package com.sprinklr.javasip.sip

Class SipExtension

java.lang.Object
com.sprinklr.javasip.sip.SipExtension
All Implemented Interfaces:
Callable<RtpAddress>, EventListener, javax.sip.SipListener
public class SipExtension extends Object implements javax.sip.SipListener, Callable<RtpAddress>
Sip entity which handles signalling on Agent's behalf. It implements SipListener which defines the methods required by an application to receive and process Events that are emitted by an object implementing the SipProvider interface.

    • processCancelRequest

      public void processCancelRequest(javax.sip.RequestEvent requestEvent, javax.sip.ServerTransaction serverTransaction)
      Process the CANCEL request, acting as UAS. A CANCEL request SHOULD NOT be sent to cancel a request other than INVITE. Refer RFC 3261. Transitions Agent's SipState to DISCONNECTED.
      Parameters:
      requestEvent - The Request event representing the CANCEL request messages that is received
